MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2004-1536. State ex rel. Harris v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 03AP-992, 2004-Ohio-4225. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

*1461IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
